  <summary date="2021-03-05T17:59:40Z" status="Introduced in House">COVID-19 Home Safety Act of 2021

This bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to report, and publish, information about injuries and deaths from consumer products during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency. The report must be submitted every three months for the duration of the emergency.</summary>
